{"tid":1985603,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"杜迪克：美斯好識欺騙 非常虛偽","createTime":"2020-04-23T09:02:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-25T05:16:32.000Z","uid":25345,"like":61,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"cc495aa6cc12a19090137df96a70ee9425777a6f","tid":1985603,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T09:02:59.000Z","msg":"前利物浦和皇馬門將杜迪克（Jerzy Dudek）在自傳中語出驚人，評價美斯（Lionel Messi）一點也不留情面。<br />\n<br />\n  杜迪克在聊到美斯時表示：「他非常的有欺騙性，而且很會挑釁人，在這一點和巴塞隆拿以及哥迪奧拿（Pep Guardiola）一樣。他們總是準備好激怒你，在這一點上他們總能做到十分完美。這一點極大的傷害了摩連奴和整個皇馬。」<br />\n<br />\n  「我曾經看到美斯對比比（Pepe）和拉莫斯（Sergio Ramos）說了很多粗魯的話，你真的很難想像，這個看上去十分安靜，貌似十分不錯的人會說這些。」"},{"pid":"8b2a331982fab4cb0fd52a157064780030d6c0c9","tid":1985603,"uid":315326,"like":32,"dislike":44,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T09:59:47.000Z","msg":"除咗皇馬Fans邊撚個會信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e5cc6dc3886277b27bf39aa6490724a55cf2085","tid":1985603,"uid":121058,"like":94,"dislike":7,"score":87,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T18:37:18.000Z","msg":"美斯對比比（Pepe）和拉莫斯（Sergio Ramos）說了很多粗魯的話<br />\n<br />\n我差D笑左出黎 <br />\n條友講出黎有無臉紅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"249f9fc6731ba60ead7c9d28b68bdbad98eb5852","tid":1985603,"uid":59818,"like":45,"dislike":1,"score":44,"quote":{"pid":"9e5cc6dc3886277b27bf39aa6490724a55cf2085","tid":1985603,"uid":121058,"like":94,"dislike":7,"score":87,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T18:37:18.000Z","msg":"美斯對比比（Pepe）和拉莫斯（Sergio Ramos）說了很多粗魯的話<br />\n<br />\n我差D笑左出黎 <br />\n條友講出黎有無臉紅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T18:39:54.000Z","msg":"原來比比拉莫斯係自衛殺人 咁唔怪得佢地"},{"pid":"0b00882b3526ef4411beec5733cd4e33e5e3d7d4","tid":1985603,"uid":85924,"like"